						               													<description>Legend of the Galactic Heroes is a wargame set in a anime universe.&amp;#10;It is based on the most popular Japanese space opera novel &amp;quot;The Galactic Heroes Legend&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ginga Eiyu Densetsu&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the distant future, the Galactic World human is divided between two major powers: &amp;quot;Reich&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Free Planets&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;Reich is under the rule of a dangerous emperor and corrupt aristocrats, while the people of the Free Planets have lost the ideals of their foundation and are under corrupt populism.&amp;#10;Both camps have no ability to destroy the enemy or to settle the war which has dragged on for hundreds of years.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But, the times have produced two geniuses of war into the same period.&amp;#10;One is &amp;quot;Reinhelt von Roengram&amp;quot;, the incomparable artist of war.&amp;#10;The other is &amp;quot;Yan Wenlee&amp;quot;, called &amp;quot;Yan the Miracle&amp;quot;, the magician of war.&amp;#10;Their appearance will change the era that they live in.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, players command Reich or Free Planets.&amp;#10;This game contains three types of space combat ship units (BB,CL,CV) and various units which appeared in the original story.&amp;#10;This game combines three types of starships, &amp;quot;Battle Ship&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Galaxy Cruiser&amp;quot;, and &amp;quot;Galaxy Fighter&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game uses a complete original system.&amp;#10;Players organize Fleets under the command of unique admirals by combining characteristics of Starships.&amp;#10;Each counter in the game is an Admiral and is rated by his fighting skills.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You use resource points to create or buy ships and put them under your admirals. The game system is very close to &amp;quot;Hitler's war&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game came out in Old Games Journal #40.</description>
